{"word":"James","slug":"james","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>James</b> - <b>(a)</b> An Apostle, son of Zebedee, brother of John<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=21'>Mat 4:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=10&verse=2'>Mat 10:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=1'>Mat 17:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=19'>Mar 1:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=3&verse=17'>Mar 3:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=5&verse=37'>Mar 5:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=2'>Mar 9:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=10&verse=35'>Mar 10:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=33'>Mar 14:33</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=10'>Luk 5:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=6&verse=14'>Luk 6:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8&verse=51'>Luk 8:51</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=13'>Act 1:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=2'>Act 12:2</a><p/><b>(b)</b> An Apostle, son of Alphaeus<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=10&verse=3'>Mat 10:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=3&verse=18'>Mar 3:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=6&verse=15'>Luk 6:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=13'>Act 1:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=18'>Act 21:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=15&verse=7'>1Co 15:7</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=1&verse=19'>Gal 1:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=2&verse=9'>Gal 2:9</a><p/><b>(c)</b> \"The Lord's Brother\" (authorities differ as to the existence<p/>and identity of this character)<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=55'>Mat 13:55</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=3'>Mar 6:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=1&verse=19'>Gal 1:19</a><p/>Characteristics of,<p/>Slow to accept Christ<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=7&verse=5'>Joh 7:5</a><p/>After the resurrection joined the disciples<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=14'>Ac 1:14</a><p/>Possibly was won by the appearance of the Lord after his resurrection<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=15&verse=7'>1Co 15:7</a><p/>Regarded by many as one of the leaders of the church at Jerusalem<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=13'>Act 15:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=18'>Act 21:18</a><p/>Also author of the epistle of James (?)<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=1&verse=1'>Jas 1:1</a>"}]}